    <sentence>
      <text>Where do you come from?</text>
      <textCn>你是哪国人？</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>I come from Greece.</text>
      <textCn>我是希腊人。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>What's the climate like in your country?</text>
      <textCn>你们国家的气候怎么样？</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>It's very pleasant.</text>
      <textCn>气候非常宜人。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>What's the weather like in spring?</text>
      <textCn>春季的天气怎么样？</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>It's often windy in March.</text>
      <textCn>3 月里常常刮风。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>It's always warm in April and May, but it rains sometimes.</text>
      <textCn>4 月和 5 月的天气总是暖洋洋的，但有时下雨。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>What's it like in summer?</text>
      <textCn>夏季的天气如何呢？</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>It's always hot in June, July and August.</text>
      <textCn>6 月、7 月和 8 月的天气总是炎热的，每天都出太阳。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>The sun shines every day.</text>
      <textCn>每天都出太阳</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>Is it cold or warm in autumn?</text>
      <textCn>秋季的天气是冷还是暖呢？</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>It's always warm in September and October.</text>
      <textCn>9 月和 10 月总是很暖和，11 月常常就冷了，而且有时下雨。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>It's often cold in November and it rains sometimes.</text>
      <textCn>11 月常常就冷了，而且有时下雨。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>Is it very cold in winter?</text>
      <textCn>冬季的天气很冷吗？</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>It's often cold in December, January and February.</text>
      <textCn>12 月、1 月和 2 月常常很冷，有时还下雪。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>It snows sometimes.</text>
      <textCn>有时还下雪。</textCn>
